  <span class="word-english">he delivers/ him</span>
  <span class="word-strongs"><a href="../lexicon/h5337.html">H5337</a></span>
</span><span class="interlinear-word" data-strongs="H3068">
  <span class="word-original hebrew">יְהוָֽה\׃</span>
