    <div class="tn-note">
      <strong>&#x1f4dd; Cultural Note:</strong> The psalmist is using the adjective **righteous** as a noun to refer to righteous people. Your language may use adjectives in the same way. If not, you could use an equivalent expression or state the meaning plainly. Alternate translation: [of the righteous people]
    </div><div class="interlinear-verse hebrew-verse"><span class="verse-num">20</span><span class="interlinear-word" data-strongs="H8104">
